 subtests)\nTest 5: Create Git Tag ✓\nTest 6: Reject Invalid Version ✓\nTest 7: Help Message ✓\n\nTotal: 12 tests passed, 0 failed\n```\n\n### 🔧 Key Features\n\n- **Version Reading**: Parses version from Go source code\n- **Version Validation**: Semantic versioning format check (vMAJOR.MINOR.PATCH)\n- **Version Update**: In-place modification of main.go\n- **Git Integration**: Creates annotated tags and commits\n- **Changelog Generation**: Creates CHANGELOG.md with structured entries\n- **Release Process**: Full automated release workflow with validation\n- **Error Handling**: Clear error messages and proper exit codes\n- **Cross-platform**: Works on macOS and Linux\n\n### 📝 Debug Log Entries\n\n- **explore1**: Discovered version stored in cmd/rick/main.go constant\n- **debug1**: Fixed macOS grep compatibility (replaced -P with sed)\n- **debug2**: Fixed validate command exit code handling (removed set -e)\n\n### 📦 Files Created/Modified\n\n- ✅ Created: `scripts/version.sh` (277 lines)\n- ✅ Created: `scripts/test_version.sh` (217 lines)\n- ✅ Updated: `.morty/plan/installation.md` (Job 5 marked complete)\n\n### 🎯 Validation Status\n\nAll verification criteria met:\n- ✅ Version numbers read correctly\n- ✅ Version numbers update correctly\n- ✅ Version format validation works\n- ✅ Git tags created successfully\n- ✅ Test script passes all 12 tests\n\n---\n\n<!-- RALPH_STATUS -->\n```json\n{\n  \"module\": \"installation\",\n  \"job\": \"job_5\",\n  \"status\": \"COMPLETED\",\n  \"tasks_completed\": 6,\n  \"tasks_total\": 6,\n  \"loop_count\": 1,\n  \"debug_issues\": 2,\n  \"debug_logs_in_plan\": true,\n  \"explore_subagent_used\": false,\n  \"summary\": \"版本管理脚本实现完成。所有6个任务已完成，12个测试全部通过。实现了版本读取、更新、验证、git tag 创建和 changelog 生成等功能。已记录2个调试日志到 Plan 文件。\"\n}\n```\n<!-- END_RALPH_STATUS -->","type":"text"}],"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"626059c6-6ed5-43a8-ba11-b43fb9784138","uuid":"aaec45e6-e5c8-47a8-89cd-916330f55959"},{"type":"result","subty